def main_keyboard() -> InlineKeyboardMarkup:
    """Use in main menu."""
    buttons = [
        [InlineKeyboardButton(text=_("chatgpt button"), callback_data="chatgpt")],
        [InlineKeyboardButton(text=_("text insert button"), callback_data="text_insert")],
        [InlineKeyboardButton(text=_("settings button"), callback_data="settings")],
        [InlineKeyboardButton(text=_("text output button"), callback_data="text_output")],
    ]
    keyboard = InlineKeyboardBuilder(markup=buttons)
    keyboard.adjust(1, 1, 2)
